                            <comment id="12951745" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2009 11:00:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And you want the id &lt;tt&gt;fileMapping&lt;/tt&gt; to be the route id?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951744" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2009 11:02:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Moving the id after the from makes the route have that id&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;from(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;jms:fileIn?transacted=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
.id(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;fileMapping&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951743" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2009 11:04:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See nabble:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/RouteBuilder%3A-Problems-with-onException-and-id-td26024958.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/RouteBuilder%3A-Problems-with-onException-and-id-td26024958.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951763" author="dulmerlucsly" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2009 12:14:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;But putting .id() before onException makes onException not working correctly&lt;br/&gt;
( see the same nabble-Thread )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951853" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2009 12:37:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Works fine on my end. Can you check this unit test.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=829770&amp;amp;view=rev&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=829770&amp;amp;view=rev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12951496" author="dulmerlucsly" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2009 09:31:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The testcase did work fine at my system, but when i change the RouteBuilder to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    @Override
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt; RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Exception {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; RouteBuilder() {
            @Override
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void configure() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Exception {
            	
            	onException(IllegalArgumentException.class).handled(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;).to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;log:bar&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mock:error&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).end();
            	 
                from(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;activemq:queue:foo?transacted=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).id(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;myCoolRoute&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
                    .transacted()
                    .choice()
                        .when(body().contains(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Kabom&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)).throwException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IllegalArgumentException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Damn&quot;&lt;/span&gt;))
                    .otherwise()
                        .to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mock:result&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
                    .end();

            }
        };
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then the test fails ....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#8211; added code snippets&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951626" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2009 11:54:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah okay yeah I can see the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Will introduce a &lt;tt&gt;routeId&lt;/tt&gt; in the DSL to use specific for setting the id of the route.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951625" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2009 11:59:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi with the latest code use the new &lt;tt&gt;routeId&lt;/tt&gt; in the DSL to set the id of the route.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;trunk: 830906.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
